Items.text: You kids are back to help me out.
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: I'm stuck in the vault... I was putting away some money but ahhhh...
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: I let the door close behind me.
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: But you guys are pros at opening the vault!
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: I'll just tell you the combination again!
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: Well I think it might be... uh...
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: But don't worry! I wrote down all the combinations for this week on a piece of paper...
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: And that piece of paper is at my house right now.
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: Could you guys go there and get it? It's the pink house in West Neighborhood. You can't miss it.
Items.name: Bank Guy

Items.text: Oh, that's close to where I live! I know where that is!
Items.name: Micycle

Items.text: Oh, thank goodness. Hurry back once you have the combination!
Items.name: Bank Guy
